{"tid":1742203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔好放棄呀","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T23:36:36.000Z","uid":291603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30a4efe77e6ab085a4151188a0130f7cb981f649","tid":1742203,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"香港人，我知道大家呢一刻都覺得好失望、沮喪，甚至睇唔到希望。<br />\n但係希望大家唔好放棄！<br />\n我哋叫有更大嘅決心去做另類抗爭，<br />\n罷中資，包括麥當勞、中銀、中國移動、華潤<br />\n罷港共爪牙，包括地鐵、國泰航空<br />\n做國際文宣，叫全世界嘅人都唾棄中國出產嘅物品<br />\n用盡所有方法斷大陸米路<br />\n我哋可能唔可以憑血肉之身擋坦克<br />\n但係我哋喺新世紀可以用智力用毅力對抗強權<br />\n滴水穿石<br />\nBe water my friend"},{"pid":"e150730052802f688d7f5718bdf3719575529638","tid":1742203,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"只係未贏，努力"},{"pid":"383a7b9fdea14a9c43b298ba4aaf6419e258a6bb","tid":1742203,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e150730052802f688d7f5718bdf3719575529638","tid":1742203,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"只係未贏，努力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨殺人無數<br />\n一定會有倒台嘅一日"},{"pid":"a2c5e000934904a694c408710da24757dea2c71b","tid":1742203,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"383a7b9fdea14a9c43b298ba4aaf6419e258a6bb","tid":1742203,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e150730052802f688d7f5718bdf3719575529638","tid":1742203,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"只係未贏，努力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨殺人無數<br />\n一定會有倒台嘅一日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T23:35:21.000Z","msg":"又爆豬瘟又爆老鼠<br />\n之後全球反共情緒上升<br />\n新彊秘密文件話唔係內鬼做都無人信 <br />\n內憂外患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05700d46641cea4055a4b38889b732445d910e2","tid":1742203,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-